<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-06-24T02:01:02+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Wed, 24 Jun 2026 02:01:02 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[xQc suspended from Twitch after FIFA World Cup 2026 copyright claim explained]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949703.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Popular streamer xQc faced a temporary 48-hour suspension from Twitch after his channel received two copyright strikes. The action stemmed from a brief clip of FIFA World Cup 2026 match footage, reportedly around five seconds long and sourced from social media.  This marks xQc's sixth suspension, highlighting ongoing debates about copyright enforcement on live-streaming platforms and the rapid dissemination of sports highlights.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/xqc-suspended-from-twitch-after-fifa-world-cup-2026-copyright-claim-explained/articleshow/131949703.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/xqc-suspended-from-twitch-after-fifa-world-cup-2026-copyright-claim-explained/articleshow/131949703.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T01:35:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131949701,imgsize-655590.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Spanish proverb of the day on ingratitude, betrayal and expectation: 'Raise crows and they will pluck out your eyes']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949508.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-proverb-of-the-day-on-ingratitude-betrayal-and-expectation-raise-crows-and-they-will-pluck-out-your-eyes/articleshow/131949508.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spanish-proverb-of-the-day-on-ingratitude-betrayal-and-expectation-raise-crows-and-they-will-pluck-out-your-eyes/articleshow/131949508.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T01:11:22+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131949557,imgsize-104830.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kylian Mbappé’s France vs Iraq World Cup highlight gets xQc suspended as FIFA issues copyright strike]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949495.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[xQc received a temporary Twitch suspension after showing a five-second Kylian Mbappé highlight from France’s World Cup match against Iraq. He said FIFA filed the DMCA claim, leading to a 24-48 hour ban. His explanation was later supported by reports from Dexerto, Sportskeeda and discussions on Reddit, all pointing to the same copyright issue.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kylian-mbapps-france-vs-iraq-world-cup-highlight-gets-xqc-suspended-as-fifa-issues-copyright-strike/articleshow/131949495.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/kylian-mbapps-france-vs-iraq-world-cup-highlight-gets-xqc-suspended-as-fifa-issues-copyright-strike/articleshow/131949495.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T01:04:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131949467,imgsize-74302.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: IShowSpeed loses it as Cristiano Ronaldo scores his first goal of the 2026 World Cup]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131949341.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Cristiano Ronaldo's first goal at the 2026 FIFA World Cup ignited an explosive reaction from superfan IShowSpeed, whose stadium celebration went viral.  The streamer's ecstatic display, fueled by his long-standing admiration for the Portuguese star, nearly overshadowed Ronaldo's brace against Uzbekistan. This moment highlights the increasing synergy between online personalities and major sporting events, captivating global audiences.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/watch-ishowspeed-loses-it-as-cristiano-ronaldo-scores-his-first-goal-of-the-2026-world-cup/articleshow/131949341.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/watch-ishowspeed-loses-it-as-cristiano-ronaldo-scores-his-first-goal-of-the-2026-world-cup/articleshow/131949341.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-24T00:53:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/e